Class CampCommitteeMemberHandler

java.lang.Object
controllers.CampCommitteeMemberHandler
public class CampCommitteeMemberHandler extends Object
Handles operations for CampCommitteeMembers related to the management of suggestions. This class provides methods to submit, delete, and edit suggestions, interfacing with the camp's database and updating the committee members' records and points accordingly.
